info.name: Paramore Icons for Tumblr Dashboard
info.description: Made from HD photos of my Paramore fan tees, edited in Photoshop to make "button" overlay. The buttons do have titles on them.
info.additionalInfo: Please don't steal. I'm happy to show you how to do this on your own if you'd like. Message me at http://banner-ful.tumblr.com/ask if you have any questions or requests.
